data.description: Wonderful farm and ranch property sitting on 16+ acres. Home boasts multiple french doors and architectual renovated remnants.  Home has 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, office, open concept with fireplace, second living area, and above ground swimming pool with a large deck. Home has waterproof floors, energy efficient smart home, end to end sunroom. Primary bath has claw foot tub, oak and quartz counters, dressing room and office and or multipurpose room with walk in. There are several outbuildings for animals with chicken coop. Two car detached garage. Property has been well thought out with an abundance of perineal plants. Unlimited wildlife is seen at this property including hogs, deer, and more. You will enjoy the privacy of the entrance rod iron gate. Great property with so many extras! Home and property are close to major highways and centrally located and only 20 mins from McKinney and 15 minutes from Bonham.
